Description.LocalizedString: The cloning process made its body wiry and fierce.
Her armored body could withstand most ammunition.
Golden growths now infested its skeletal frame.
Its skeletal frame was especially pronounced.
Two brutal minds fused into one.
The size of the crest was a display of her power.
Several injections were required to pierce the hardened exterior and reach the tissue beneath.
Its slick skin reflected the moonlight.
The specimen was strong enough to escape its restraints.
A weapon fit for a queen.
Its unforgiving claws were stained with serum.
The talons of a worthy adversary.
